; Seasonal Hunting Area: Summer. Difficulty: moderately to very difficult.
;
; Forget the better mousetrap. It's time to build a better mouse.
;
MNUMBER 206
NAME rat
ADJECTIVE 80
PART 0
PART 1
PART 2
PART 9
PART 10
PART 11
PART 12
PART 17
PART 18
PART 19
*DESCRIPTION_START
This furtive rodent is no larger than a normal rat, but the red eyes
glowing like two tiny embers suggest a deadly difference. As it darts
across the occasional patch of dim light, it seems to be formed out of
pure shadow... yet casts no shadow itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
