;
; It's a super will-o-the-wisp. Why wait for what you can go get for yourself?
;
MNUMBER 236
NAME mistwraith
ADJECTIVE 26
PART 0
PART 1
PART 5
PART 6
PART 7
PART 8
*DESCRIPTION_START
The mistwraith looks much like an unusually large will-o-the-wisp at first
glance, except for its ruddy coloration. Closer examination reveals a
vaguely humanoid form curled in a fetal position within it, but the churning
luminous mist around it hides further details from view.
*DESCRIPTION_END
