MNUMBER 245
NAME bloodscourge
PART 0
PART 1
PART 2
PART 5
PART 6
PART 7
PART 8
PART 13
PART 14
PART 17
PART 18
PART 19
*DESCRIPTION_START
Howls of mingled anguish and fury peal from this monstrosity as it stalks
about on its powerful beastlike legs. Long sharp horns rise from the temples
of its almost-human head through its tangled gray hair. Its insane crimson
eyes, constantly weeping bloody tears, glare wildly around searching for
something living with which to share its misery.
*DESCRIPTION_END
