;
; The darkweaver is the most versatile denizen, and quite tough.
;
MNUMBER 62
NAME darkweaver
PART 0
PART 1
PART 5
PART 6
PART 7
PART 8
PART 13
PART 14
*DESCRIPTION_START
Garments woven of silken shadows whisper quietly as the darkweaver moves,
cloaking the tall, slender figure in darkness and disguising gender. There
is something akin to an aelf in the brief glimpses of its comely, angular
features and intense silver gaze. But its skin and flowing hair are of
deepest black, making it difficult to see in the darkness it calls home.
*DESCRIPTION_END
