;
; So much for cuteness. The unicorn will guard the darkweaver, by the way.
;
MNUMBER 63
NAME unicorn
ADJECTIVE 2
PART 0
PART 1
PART 2
PART 9
PART 10
PART 11
PART 12
PART 17
*DESCRIPTION_START
In most aspects it resembles the unicorn of legend, with a slender equine
head and body, sharp cloven hooves, lion's tail, and a single spiral horn
rising from the center of its forehead. But from sleek muzzle to tufted
tailtip, this creature is absolute, lightless black. The blazing bluegreen
radiance of its eyes reflects along the length of its dark, iridescent
horn. It is built for battle, with deadly spikes of bone projecting at
many major joints.
*DESCRIPTION_END
